title: Stylized Fantasy Newbie Outfits Pack

Asset Description:

THIS ASSET IS AN ADDITIONAL PACKAGE FOR

1)Human Female

Different color materials for each equipment component for wide armor and weapon color customization are included.

Also includes a preview material for character assets.
